/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Schematic overview 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Real example 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-F2049DB3-F30D-4CAF-B617-58057AF98324" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-4645D193-CF90-4C3B-AF58-E8826B53B714-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4645D193-CF90-4C3B-AF58-E8826B53B714-low.png"/></fig></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-C976F503-16E5-49A6-9965-B984E79BB952" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4791356B-C59F-4350-A976-4C9D45A27C0F-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4791356B-C59F-4350-A976-4C9D45A27C0F-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-A0A27984-F97C-4544-AC11-38CF6F329CB1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-5D446CFF-A30A-4A5D-BF22-52052A66340E-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-5D446CFF-A30A-4A5D-BF22-52052A66340E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-EC1EAE23-40EC-4B10-A2C9-83873F76DC70" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Collect</title><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Symptoms</b> 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The position of the image relative to the media edge is drifting 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Drifting is step-wise (approx. 1-2 mm) 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Drifting can be temporary (only a few swaths) 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Functional logging (if available)</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No logging available which can pinpoint to this case. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ADAM-triggers</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No ADAM triggers are available 
</p></section><section id="GUID-242D76E3-E255-4E85-A323-10B9BE31488C" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/></section><section id="GUID-DDCC1BB0-B402-4010-9156-67DB737F3DE5" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Analyze/Repair</title><fig id="GUID-5C923CEE-B419-4381-9667-3C115F5AE35A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B6FD9C65-A02D-4780-ABE9-A7668E527B72-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B6FD9C65-A02D-4780-ABE9-A7668E527B72-svg.svg"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-BB9BDDD1-E29C-42C5-BF10-2854E3AE4223" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Steps explanation</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-D963269B-E108-446A-A212-4581FEAA8740" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="1.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="2.01*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="3.37*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="3.68*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Type 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">To do 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check if the ruler is polluted. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Clean ruler. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Use IPA to clean the ruler 
</p><note id="GUID-F7153B4A-A60E-4664-8EE5-6200012B75DF" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Only rulers which contain a green sticker on the left-side can be cleaned. 
</p></note></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check whether the ruler is correctly placed in the guidance. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EF126F31-C2F6-4E85-87FE-73E87CAD74B2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-9624EB6C-03A3-43D4-872E-F1407B7AD419-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-9624EB6C-03A3-43D4-872E-F1407B7AD419-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place ruler in guidance. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Replace the ruler. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-2513E5DF-C282-453D-9841-6E539DB0EB51" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Evaluate/Prevention</title><p class="- topic/p ">Do not touch or damage the ruler. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-987F83F9-80F0-41BC-B82B-BB16DA268203" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Background info</title><p class="- topic/p ">The ruler contains of a transparent strip which has small markings on it. These markings are used by the printhead carriage to determine it’s position during printing. If these markings are damaged or not visible due to pollution the encoder might interpreted the markings wrong and the position might shift. In case the markings can not be read at all a MRE5709 occurs. (Carriage position error). 
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-00803BE3-C849-4315-B1B2-2BBE04B8DBA4.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Solutions</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
